    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "can u just tell me if it's actually possible to overdose that fast? i'm not trying to do anything crazy, just trying to feel better. like if i take the 50k for two weeks and then stop, is there really a high chance i'm actually gonna end up with kidney issues? it seems a bit extreme to say it's that dangerous for just a fortnight.",
